Clean the Data

head(Cleaned_fifa_data)
Top<-
  Cleaned_fifa_data%>%
  mutate(rank=rank(desc(Overall))) %>%
  filter(rank<1000)%>%
  mutate("region"=Nationality)
 
Top
Grouped_top <-
  Top %>%
  group_by(region) %>%
  summarise(count=n())
Grouped_top

Join

World_map<- map_data("world")
Joined_top <-
  World_map %>%
  left_join(Grouped_top)
Joining, by = "region"
Joined_top

Create Function

top_soccer_function <-function(x){
  
  Top<-
  Cleaned_fifa_data%>%
  mutate(rank=rank(desc(Overall))) %>%
  filter(rank<x) %>%
  mutate("region"=Nationality)
  
  Grouped_top <-
  Top %>%
  group_by(region) %>%
  summarise(count=n())
  
  World_map<- map_data("world")
  
  Joined_top <-
  World_map %>%
  left_join(Grouped_top)
  
  Map<-
    ggplot(Joined_top, aes(x = long, y = lat, group=group)) +
    geom_polygon(aes(fill=count), colour = "white")+
    scale_fill_viridis_c(option = "C")
  
  return(Map)
}
top_soccer_function(100)
Joining, by = "region"
